<author>Knapp, Phoebe P. (1839-1908), Crosby, Fanny Jane (1820-1915)</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
.   C              Dm   C
 Anyq senemin, meniń Isam,
.F         G         C
 Aspannyń murasyn berdi maǵan.
.      C         Dm   C
 Meni jubatyp, qýantady.
.    F      G      C
 Ielenemin sol murany.

[C1]
.      C          F       C
   // Saltanat ándi aıtam máńgi,
.           Dm        G
   Meniń ǵajap Isam týraly!  //

[V2]
 Jan-tánimmen Oǵan berildim,
 Isanyń perzenti endi boldym.
 Tek odan tabam nan men sýsyn,
 Tynyshtyqqa toldy júregim.

[V3]
 Pana boldy kúshti qolymen,
 Oǵan batyl anyq senemin men.
 Qıyndyqta da rýhym rıza,
 Ǵajap Dosym, máńgi qasymda.

[V4]
 Senimen ǵana tabar rýhym,
 Ǵajapqa toly ómir men tynym.
 Men kishireıip, Sen ósesiń.
 Saǵan júregimdi bereıin.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>Anyq senemin, meniń Isam РӘЖ174</title>
</song>